actions.committee: Senate Committee on Rules and Administration
actions.text: Referred to Senate Committee on Rules and Administration.
Reported to Senate from the Committee on Rules and Administration, S. Rept. 93-833.

official_title: Resolved, that the committee print of the Committee on the Judiciary entitled "Freedom of Information Act Source Book: Legislative Materials, Cases, Articles" be printed as a Senate document.

summary.text: Provides that the committe print of the Senate Committee on the Judiciary entitled "Freedom of Information Act Source Book: Legislative Materials, Cases, Articles" be printed as a Senate document; and that there be printed for the use of that committee 1,300 additional copies of such document.
